### Problem:

Since the latest Flutter versions, users have reported that animations are super fast. We found that this issue is connected to the developer setting on Android: "Transition animation scale". If this setting is set to "OFF," Flutter animations happen instantly, which completely destroys the user experience.
Of course, not everyone has Developer Settings enabled, but regardless, please treat "Transition animation scale - OFF" the same way as in previous versions, where it was not a problem. Simply set it to Animation Scale x1 for example. 

### Expected results

Normal animation speed

### Actual results

Animations are instand

