### Use case

We use local_auth plugin which used androidx Biometric on Android.

androidx biometric force use fragment Activity, so we change our super class to FlutterFragmentActivity.

Previously, we override `getCachedEngineId` to used cached fragment, but this result in blank screen after put app in background for over one night.

Then we  remove `getCachedEngineId`, and use override of `provideFlutterEngine`.

Recently, when using monkey test on Android, we found crash log for flutter fragment like this:

